msgctxt "72_Rowdy Homeless Man"
msgid "A kappa in Kamurocho? I'll drink to that!"
msgstr "Un kappa a Kamurocho? Ci bevo sopra!"

msgctxt "84_Skeptical Homeless Man"
msgid ""
"There ain't no such thing as kappas! You were just drunk- "
"and still are!"
msgstr "I kappa non esistono proprio! Eri solo ubriaco... e lo sei ancora!"

msgctxt "96_Rowdy Homeless Man"
msgid "I'm telling you what I saw. It was an alien or something!"
msgstr "Ti sto dicendo quello che ho visto. Era un alieno o roba del genere!"

msgctxt "108_Skeptical Homeless Man"
msgid "There's no such thing as aliens! You're just drunk."
msgstr "Gli alieni non esistono proprio! Sei solo sbronzo."

msgctxt "120_Rowdy Homeless Man"
msgid ""
"Well, maybe it was a monster! Ever think of that? "
"I mean, shit, you didn't even see it."
msgstr "Beh, e se fosse stato un mostro? Ci hai mai pensato? Voglio dire, cazzo, non l'hai neanche visto!"

msgctxt "132_Skeptical Homeless Man"
msgid "Then what'd it look like, this alien-monster of yours?"
msgstr "E allora, com'era fatto questo tuo mostro alieno?"

msgctxt "144_Rowdy Homeless Man"
msgid ""
"It was green, and kinda slimy. It lifted the manhole "
"cover in Children's Park and glared right at me!"
msgstr "Era verde, e mezzo viscido. Ha sollevato il tombino del Children's Park e mi ha fissato in cagnesco!"

msgctxt "156_Skeptical Homeless Man"
msgid ""
"That, my friend, was a kappa. You know, those mythical, cucumber-eating "
"critters. Congrats on finding such a fantastic beast."
msgstr "Quello, amico mio, era un kappa. Sai, quelle creature mitologiche amanti dei cetrioli. Complimenti per aver scovato un animale così fantastico."

msgctxt "168_Rowdy Homeless Man"
msgid ""
"So, okay, it was a kappa! Doesn't matter what it's called. When I think of "
"that... <Italic>thing</Italic> creeping through the streets, well, it drives"
" a man to drink!"
msgstr "E va bene, allora era un kappa! Non importa come si chiama. Quando penso a quella... <Italic>cosa</Italic> che si aggira per le skates, beh, spinge un uomo a bere!"

msgctxt "180_Skeptical Homeless Man"
msgid ""
"I told you, there ain't no such thing as kappas! "
"I swear..."
msgstr "Ti dico che i kappa non esistono proprio! Giuro..."